            </Observed_Example>
            <Observed_Example>
               <Reference>CVE-2001-1559</Reference>
               <Description>Chain: System call returns wrong value (CWE-393), leading to a resultant NULL dereference (CWE-476).</Description>
               <Link>https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-2001-1559</Link>
            </Observed_Example>
            <Observed_Example>
               <Reference>CVE-2003-0187</Reference>
               <Description>Program uses large timeouts on unconfirmed connections resulting from inconsistency in linked lists implementations.</Description>
               <Link>https://www.cve.org/CVERecord?id=CVE-2003-0187</Link>
            </Observed_Example>
            <Observed_Example>
               <Reference>CVE-1999-1446</Reference>
               <Description>UI inconsistency; visited URLs list not cleared when "Clear History" option is selected.</Description>
